Bankia to Raise About EU1 Billion With Commercial Paper Issue

-- B y   C h a r l e s   P e n t y
-- 
2011-09-23T11:30:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/bankia-to-raise-about-eu1-billion-with-commercial-paper-issue.html
Bankia will raise about 1 billion
euros with a sale of  commercial paper  to clients including
retail customers that will yield up to 4 percent a year, the
bank said in a statement sent by email. The sale is part of a
commercial paper program of as much as 5 billion euros, the bank
said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Charles Penty at 
 cpenty@bloomberg.net  